---
title: Quick All-American Chicken & Slaw Tacos with Smashed Avocado & Smokey Aioli
description: Time for another tantalizing taco-tastic meal! This version isn’t the most authentic, but it’s definitely delicious, with All American-spiced chicken, fresh slaw and smokey aioli wrapped in a warm tortilla. Give this handheld delight a try!
